		<hr size="1">I wanna make a Bard, I rarely get characters past level 50, so don't bother with any post 50 talk : ) the things I'm torn between are these:</P><P>1.Which Server?, This is narrowed down to, Rallos Zek, which I have lots of experience on but only encountered a single Bard, I was a roleplaying Ogre Beastlord and attacked at the sight of him and he got away once my blind wore off and the next got resisted and the next was Target is out of Range, he was gone : ) I'm wondering what the existence of a Bard on Rallos Zek is like, is it just running away from PvP whenever a battle ensues?, I don't want to live in fear, I want to be able to duke it out.</P><P>The other server is just simply a blue server, I can't decide between Firiona Vie, Stromm, or just my normal Karana, but this doesn't need to be discussed, if I don't play on Rallos I'll pikk one of these on my own.</P><P>So anything that you think could help sway my sever choice is much welcome, thank you : )</P><P></P><P>2.The other thing I am torn between is my race. The two choices I have it down to are Half Elf and Vah shir.</P><P>Since I don't believe in twinking, the Half Elf newbie Armor is really looking nice to me and I don't think Vah Shir have newbie armor</P><P>Vah Shir sounds really fun though because I have never made a Vah shir before and like their power and looks, while I don't too much care for Half Elf looks much. This will probly make everybody say then Vah shir is the one for you but I'm fine with playing a Half elf if it's obviously better. </P><P>I think I could get away with going Vah Shir on a blue server since stats don't matter as much, but it seems like I would have to go with the Half Elf on Rallos. What do you think?</P><P>Yikes, Thanks to anybody that even took the time to read that, let alone respond to it hehe, I wanna make him as soon as possible, Wednesday at the latest.</P><P>Thank You : )<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
